	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You hold up a cocoon containing a metamorphizing pupa and, with a whisper, rotate it, and as you do, your target is transformed into a different species.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save wisdom]]{Wisdom Save}</strong></p><p>This spell has no effect on a shapeshifter or a creature with 0 hit points.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The target is transformed into the form of a CR 0 &amp;reference[beast].</p><ul><li><p>The target's statistics are replaced by the new form, including their ability scores, armor class, skills, movement, and actions they can perform.</p></li><li><p>The target's personality and memories are partially intact, but their intelligence is low enough that they cannot read, write, or speak.</p></li><li><p>The target's gear melds into the new form, and they cannot use any of their equipment.</p></li><li><p>The target gains 10 temporary hit points*. When they lose all temporary hit points, they revert to their original form and any excess damage is applied to the original form's hit points.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase temporary hit points by 10 for each spell level above 4th.</p><p></p><p><strong>Note: This spell is not automated, but it should be in an upcoming update. Currently it only rolls the save and adds temporary hit points.</strong></p>",
			"chat": ""
		},
